---
import Base from "../../layouts/Base.astro";
import Header from "../../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/Footer.astro";

const title = "Best TOEFL Online Courses 2026: Top 8 Rated Programs";
const description = "Discover the best TOEFL online courses to boost your score. We compare the top 8 programs based on price, study materials, and score guarantees.";
---

<Base title={title} description={description} type="article" publishedTime="2026-04-11">
 <Header />
 <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 text-neutral-300">
 <div class="mb-12">
 <span class="text-sm text-indigo-400 font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider">Resource Guide · Updated April 2026</span>
 <h1 class="text-5xl font-extrabold text-white mt-4 mb-6 leading-tight">Best TOEFL Online Courses: Top 8 Picks for 2026</h1>
 <p class="text-xl text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed">Finding the right TOEFL prep course can save you weeks of wasted study time. With so many options available, it is hard to know which one actually delivers results. We have analyzed dozens of programs to bring you the 8 best TOEFL online courses for every budget and learning style.</p>
 </div>

 <div class="space-y-12">
 <!-- Course 1 -->
 <div class="bg-neutral-800 border border-neutral-700 rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg">
 <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center justify-between mb-6">
 <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">1. Magoosh TOEFL</h2>
 <span class="bg-green-600 text-white text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full mt-2 md:mt-0 w-fit">Best Overall Value</span>
 </div>
 <p class="mb-6 leading-relaxed">Magoosh is famous for its high-quality video lessons and affordable pricing. It offers a comprehensive dashboard that tracks your progress and predicts your score. With over 420 practice questions and detailed explanations for every answer, it is a favorite for students who want a structured path without a high price tag.</p>
 <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-6">
 <div class="bg-neutral-900 p-4 rounded-xl">
 <p class="text-sm text-neutral-400 font-bold uppercase">Pricing</p>
 <p class="text-white font-semibold">Starts at $129</p>
 </div>
 <div class="bg-neutral-900 p-4 rounded-xl">
 <p class="text-sm text-neutral-400 font-bold uppercase">Best For</p>
 <p class="text-white font-semibold">Self-motivated learners</p>
 </div>
 </div>
 <ul class="space-y-2 mb-8">
 <li class="flex items-center"><span class="text-green-500 mr-2"></span> 4-point score guarantee</li>
 <li class="flex items-center"><span class="text-green-500 mr-2"></span> 7-day money-back guarantee</li>
 </ul>
 <a href="/reviews/magoosh-toefl/" class="text-blue-400 font-bold hover:underline">Read our full Magoosh TOEFL review →</a>
 </div>

 <!-- Course 2 -->
 <div class="bg-neutral-800 border border-neutral-700 rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg">
 <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center justify-between mb-6">
 <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">2. BestMyTest TOEFL</h2>
 <span class="bg-blue-600 text-white text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full mt-2 md:mt-0 w-fit">Best for Practice Tests</span>
 </div>
 <p class="mb-6 leading-relaxed">If you want to simulate the real test environment, BestMyTest is the top choice. They offer 20 full-length practice tests and over 2,000 practice questions. Their "TOEFL Tutor" system uses AI to analyze your speaking and writing, providing instant feedback that helps you identify weak spots quickly.</p>
 <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-6">
 <div class="bg-neutral-900 p-4 rounded-xl">
 <p class="text-sm text-neutral-400 font-bold uppercase">Pricing</p>
 <p class="text-white font-semibold">Starts at $69/month</p>
 </div>
 <div class="bg-neutral-900 p-4 rounded-xl">
 <p class="text-sm text-neutral-400 font-bold uppercase">Best For</p>
 <p class="text-white font-semibold">Intensive practice</p>
 </div>
 </div>
 <ul class="space-y-2 mb-8">
 <li class="flex items-center"><span class="text-green-500 mr-2"></span>Massive question bank</li>
 <li class="flex items-center"><span class="text-green-500 mr-2"></span>Integrated speaking and writing feedback</li>
 </ul>
 <a href="/reviews/bestmytest-toefl/" class="text-blue-400 font-bold hover:underline">Read our full BestMyTest TOEFL review →</a>
 </div>

 <!-- Course 3 -->
 <div class="bg-neutral-800 border border-neutral-700 rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg">
 <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center justify-between mb-6">
 <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">3. See Guru TOEFL Tutors</h2>
 <span class="bg-yellow-600 text-white text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full mt-2 md:mt-0 w-fit">Best for 1-on-1 Help</span>
 </div>
 <p class="mb-6 leading-relaxed">Sometimes a video course is not enough. See Guru connects you with certified TOEFL tutors who can provide personalized feedback on your speaking and writing. This is the most effective way to break through a score plateau. You can book lessons whenever you want, focusing exactly on the skills you find most difficult.</p>
 <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-6">
 <div class="bg-neutral-900 p-4 rounded-xl">
 <p class="text-sm text-neutral-400 font-bold uppercase">Pricing</p>
 <p class="text-white font-semibold">From $5/hour</p>
 </div>
 <div class="bg-neutral-900 p-4 rounded-xl">
 <p class="text-sm text-neutral-400 font-bold uppercase">Best For</p>
 <p class="text-white font-semibold">Personalized coaching</p>
 </div>
 </div>
 <a href="/go/see-guru/" rel="sponsored nofollow" class="inline-block bg-blue-600 text-white font-bold px-6 py-3 rounded-xl hover:bg-blue-900/300 transition-colors">Find a TOEFL Tutor on See Guru</a>
 </div>

 <!-- Course 4 -->
 <div class="bg-neutral-800 border border-neutral-700 rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg">
 <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6">4. Kaplan TOEFL iBT Prep</h2>
 <p class="mb-6 leading-relaxed">Kaplan is a giant in the test prep industry. Their TOEFL course is known for being very thorough and professional. It includes a mobile app for studying on the go and access to their "Smart Reports" which analyze your performance. It is a more expensive option, but the quality of the curriculum is world-class.</p>
 <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-6">
 <div class="bg-neutral-900 p-4 rounded-xl">
 <p class="text-sm text-neutral-400 font-bold uppercase">Pricing</p>
 <p class="text-white font-semibold">Starts at $349</p>
 </div>
 <div class="bg-neutral-900 p-4 rounded-xl">
 <p class="text-sm text-neutral-400 font-bold uppercase">Best For</p>
 <p class="text-white font-semibold">Comprehensive study</p>
 </div>
 </div>
 </div>

 <!-- Course 5 -->
 <div class="bg-neutral-800 border border-neutral-700 rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg">
 <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6">5. ETS Official TOEFL Courses</h2>
 <p class="mb-6 leading-relaxed">Who knows the test better than the people who create it? ETS offers several official prep options, including the "TOEFL iBT Free Practice Test" and paid "Official Guide" books. Their online courses are direct and follow the exact logic of the actual exam. They are essential for understanding the specific scoring criteria used by graders.</p>
 <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-6">
 <div class="bg-neutral-900 p-4 rounded-xl">
 <p class="text-sm text-neutral-400 font-bold uppercase">Pricing</p>
 <p class="text-white font-semibold">Varies (Free to $100+)</p>
 </div>
 <div class="bg-neutral-900 p-4 rounded-xl">
 <p class="text-sm text-neutral-400 font-bold uppercase">Best For</p>
 <p class="text-white font-semibold">Authentic materials</p>
 </div>
 </div>
 </div>

 <!-- Course 6 -->
 <div class="bg-neutral-800 border border-neutral-700 rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg">
 <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6">6. Udemy: TOEFL iBT Complete Course</h2>
 <p class="mb-6 leading-relaxed">Udemy has hundreds of TOEFL courses, but the "TOEFL iBT Complete Online Preparation Course" by Maria Becker is a standout. It covers all four sections in detail and is frequently on sale for under $20. It is a great choice for students on a tight budget who still want a complete video-based curriculum.</p>
 <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-6">
 <div class="bg-neutral-900 p-4 rounded-xl">
 <p class="text-sm text-neutral-400 font-bold uppercase">Pricing</p>
 <p class="text-white font-semibold">Often under $20</p>
 </div>
 <div class="bg-neutral-900 p-4 rounded-xl">
 <p class="text-sm text-neutral-400 font-bold uppercase">Best For</p>
 <p class="text-white font-semibold">Budget-conscious students</p>
 </div>
 </div>
 </div>

 <!-- Course 7 -->
 <div class="bg-neutral-800 border border-neutral-700 rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg">
 <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6">7. PrepScholar TOEFL</h2>
 <p class="mb-6 leading-relaxed">PrepScholar uses a "customized learning" approach. Their algorithm identifies your weaknesses and creates a study plan just for you. They are so confident in their method that they offer a 15-point score increase guarantee. If you want a course that adapts to your specific needs, this is a strong contender.</p>
 <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-6">
 <div class="bg-neutral-900 p-4 rounded-xl">
 <p class="text-sm text-neutral-400 font-bold uppercase">Pricing</p>
 <p class="text-white font-semibold">Starts at $187</p>
 </div>
 <div class="bg-neutral-900 p-4 rounded-xl">
 <p class="text-sm text-neutral-400 font-bold uppercase">Best For</p>
 <p class="text-white font-semibold">Adaptive learning</p>
 </div>
 </div>
 </div>

 <!-- Course 8 -->
 <div class="bg-neutral-800 border border-neutral-700 rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg">
 <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6">8. italki TOEFL Prep</h2>
 <p class="mb-6 leading-relaxed">Similar to See Guru, italki is a marketplace for language tutors. You can find hundreds of teachers who specialize in TOEFL preparation. The advantage of italki is the sheer number of tutors available at all hours. You can easily find a teacher who shares your native language to explain difficult English concepts more clearly.</p>
 <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-6">
 <div class="bg-neutral-900 p-4 rounded-xl">
 <p class="text-sm text-neutral-400 font-bold uppercase">Pricing</p>
 <p class="text-white font-semibold">From $8/hour</p>
 </div>
 <div class="bg-neutral-900 p-4 rounded-xl">
 <p class="text-sm text-neutral-400 font-bold uppercase">Best For</p>
 <p class="text-white font-semibold">Native speaker practice</p>
 </div>
 </div>
 <a href="/go/italki" rel="sponsored nofollow" class="text-blue-400 font-bold hover:underline">Find an italki tutor →</a>
 </div>
 </div>

 <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mt-20 mb-8">How to Choose the Right TOEFL Course</h2>
 <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-16">
 <div class="bg-neutral-800 p-6 rounded-xl border border-neutral-700">
 <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">1. Know Your Goal</h3>
 <p>If you only need to improve by 5 points, a budget course like Magoosh is enough. If you need a 20-point jump, consider a 1-on-1 tutor.</p>
 </div>
 <div class="bg-neutral-800 p-6 rounded-xl border border-neutral-700">
 <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">2. Check the Format</h3>
 <p>Do you learn better from videos, books, or live sessions? Choose a course that matches your learning style to stay motivated.</p>
 </div>
 <div class="bg-neutral-800 p-6 rounded-xl border border-neutral-700">
 <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">3. Look for Guarantees</h3>
 <p>Courses with score guarantees show they are confident in their curriculum. It also gives you peace of mind regarding your investment.</p>
 </div>
 </div>

 <div class="bg-neutral-800 border border-neutral-700 rounded-2xl p-10 text-center">
 <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Still Not Sure Which One to Pick?</h2>
 <p class="text-lg mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Our editorial team recommends starting with a diagnostic practice test. This will show you exactly where you stand and which skills need the most work.</p>
 <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-4">
 <a href="/resources/free-toefl-practice-tests/" class="bg-blue-600 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold hover:bg-blue-900/30 transition-colors">Find Free Practice Tests</a>
 <a href="/go/see-guru/" rel="sponsored nofollow" class="bg-neutral-700 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold hover:bg-neutral-600 transition-colors">Talk to a Study Advisor</a>
 </div>
 </div>
 
 <aside class="mt-12 mb-8 p-6 bg-slate-900/60 border border-slate-700 rounded-xl">
 <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-4">Related TOEFL resources</h3>
 <ul class="space-y-2 text-base">
